    @Mojo(name="purge",
      defaultPhase=GENERATE_RESOURCES,
      threadSafe=true,
      requiresDependencyResolution=NONE,
      requiresOnline=true,
      aggregator=true)
public class PurgeMojo
extends BaseDependencyCheckMojo
    Maven Plugin that purges the local copy of the NVD data.
